data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  Don't miss this Large Family Home in Desirable Emerald Hills! A super spacious 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home nestled on a large lot with a 2 car garage and huge screened in porch! This home has good bones and the open floor plan offers numerous possibilities waiting for your finishing designer touch! There are 2 living areas including a family room with a corner fireplace open to the large kitchen! This split bedroom layout has a spacious owners suite with walkin closets, dual sinks, garden tub and shower plus there's 2 guest bedrooms 1/2 bath & a 2nd full bath! You'll be ALL WEATHER READY with a PROPANE GENERATOR! This Rockledge location is conveniently located close to Viera Shopping, Restaurants, the Beach, KSC, the Port & 40 minutes to OIA!
